.SH NAME
kpseaccess \- determine whether a gangbangin' file can be accessed
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B kpseaccess
.I mode
.I file
.\"=====================================================================
.SH DESCRIPTION
Exit successfully if
.I file
can be accessed wit tha specified
.IR mode .
The
.I mode
is a optionizzle dash
.RB (` \- ')
followed by zero or mo' lettas of
.BR rwx ,
where
.B r
is fo' readable,
.B w
is fo' writable, and
.B x
is fo' executable.
.PP
